headline: TE Connectivity (NYSE:TEL) Enhances Shareholder Value With 9% Dividend Increase
summary: TE Connectivity (NYSE:TEL) recently announced a 9% increase in its quarterly dividend, amplifying the company's commitment to returning value to its shareholders despite facing a 14% decline in share price over the past week. This drop coincided with broader market turmoil, highlighted by a massive 9.4% decline precipitated by President Trump's tariff announcements. Additionally, the company is embroiled in a patent infringement lawsuit filed by Credo Technology. While such legal challenges...
